article_title: Can Chicago's Tech Community Carry Rahm Emanuel To Victory?

article_metadata.description: If there is a campaign success story Chicago’s embattled Mayor Rahm Emanuel can point to as an example of how he helped recruit jobs, companies and innovation to the city he wants to run for another four years, it’s technology.
